tool_description: This API retrieves physical quantities,constants and equations formatted as JSON
title: Physical quantities, constants and equations

api_list.name: Get equations
api_list.description: This endpoint return back data of equations formatted as JSON
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://physical-quantities-constants-and-equations.p.rapidapi.com/equations/"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "physical-quantities-constants-and-equations.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())
